description:
This is a 30 minute workout called 'HIIT BEYOND | LES MILLS GRIT x Reebok 30-minute HIIT workout' from the channel Les Mills.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Other/Cardio.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Extreme.

Original workout description: Les Mills and Reebok have teamed up to bring you a free LES MILLS GRIT Cardio workout highlighting all the benefits of their first and only training shoe designed for high-intensity interval training! No equipment needed.
LES MILLS GRIT Cardio is a 30-minute HIIT workout that improves cardiovascular fitness, increases speed and maximizes calorie burn. Get ready to up the intensity. 

Try LES MILLS On Demand FREE for 14 days here: https://lmod.co/onlineworkouts

Try HIIT workouts at home on LES MILLS On Demand: https://www.lesmills.com/ondemand/workouts/hiit/
